    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "DATE: August 13, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, NEWARK",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISC REPORTED AT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "HACKENSACK, NEW JERSEY",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "AUGUST 3, 1947 - MISCELLANEOUS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Reference is made to the teletype from the Newark Division",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "to the Bureau dated August 4, 1947 stating that a \"Flying Disc\" had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "been reported to have been seen at Hackensack, New Jersey on August 3 b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "last by one [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Hackensack, upon",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "interview by Special Agent [REDACTED] of this Division, stated",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "that on August 3 he had been standing with [REDACTED] a soldier",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "stationed at Fort Dix, observing a \"ham\" radio rig atop a two-story b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "house on Simons Avenue, Hackensack. It was approximately 7:45 p.m.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "and they were in this vicinity for the purpose of meeting [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "girlfriend, one [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "[REDACTED] commented to [REDACTED] that a child has apparently",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "lost its balloon. [REDACTED] looked and about a block or a half block",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "away noticed a round, black object moving from south to north and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "east of the stop where he and [REDACTED] were standing. [REDACTED] noticed",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "that it was moving too fast to be an ordinary balloon, but he could",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "not discern whether it was globular in form or a disc. He said it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "was about thirty to forty inches in diameter moving north in a hori-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "zontal plane about two hundred yards above the top of the hill at b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "Summit Avenue and Simons Avenue. It proceeded at a steady rate,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "emitted no rays, and was moving fast enough to require them to turn",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "their heads steadily in order to follow it. [REDACTED] girlfriend came",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "out about fifteen seconds after they first sighted it. They pointed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "it out to her, and she said that it looked like a bird on the horizon",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "so small. It faded out of sight shortly thereafter. [REDACTED] said",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "that a line drawn along its apparent course of flight would go from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "the vicinity of Bendix, New Jersey to a point west of Westwood, New",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "Jersey.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "[REDACTED] also said that a man on the porch across the street",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "also noticed it and pointed it out to the women. [REDACTED] said that b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "this man seemed excited but did nothing about it.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "[REDACTED] said that he was positive it was no optical illusion.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "He was not facing into the sun and saw the object clearly. He also b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "said that he would have thought nothing of it except for the speed at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "which it was traveling.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
